Package socialmedia

Class GenericPost

java.lang.Object
socialmedia.Post
socialmedia.GenericPost
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class GenericPost
extends Post
The class that represents a generic post in this social media app that comments can be redirected to if their parent posts have been deleted.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Hayden, Jorel
